OCL: 
	1. Components: Costs >=0
	2. ItemTypes: size(name) >0
	3. Service: Reliability [0..1]
	4. ItemGenerator ItemType == OutputSlot ItemType
	5. WasteStore and ProductStore: Capacity > 0 
	6. WasteStore and ProductStore: Capacity >= ItemTypes
	7. Connected slots must specify the same item types
	8. The connector has to be defined in the area that also contains the component owning the connected output